videoSnippet.title: Chinese Superstar | Ding Liren vs Duda | Batumi Chess Olympiad (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Ding Liren vs Jan-Krzysztof Duda
43rd Chess Olympiad (2018), rd 9, Oct-04 
Queen's Gambit Declined: Vienna Variation (D39)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 e6 3. Nf3 d5 4. Nc3 dc4 5. e4 b5 6. e5 Nd5 7. Nb5 Nb6 8. Be2 Nc6 9. O-O Be7 10. Qd2 O-O 11. Qf4 Rb8 12. Nc3 f5 13. Qg3 Kh8 14. Rd1 Nb4 15. b3 cb3 16. ab3 a6 17. Bc4 Nc2 18. Ra2 Nb4 19. Ra1 Nc2 20. Ra2 Nb4 21. Re2 a5 22. d5 ed5 23. e6 Bd6 24. Qh3 Qf6 25. Nb5 dc4 26. Nd6 cd6 27. e7 Re8 28. Ng5 Qg6 29. Rd6 f4 30. Qh4 Qb1 31. Re1 Bf5 32. Rd8 Bg6 33. Rb8 Rb8 34. Qf4 Rg8 35. Nf7 Bf7 36. Qf7 Nd7 37. e8Q Nf6 38. Bg5
